#circuitbreakersg day 48

It’s almost time for the next groceries run so I have very limited ingredients left in the fridge. Decided to make something simple for brunch and we ended up with some fluffy omelette. 😃
.
.
.
My first attempt making this dish many weeks ago was not successful as I didn’t beat the egg whites long enough. .
.
.
Today’s attempt was much better.. except that omelette was fluffier when I was just done cooking it but I took a while to take the pictures so the egg sank a little.. 😔
.
.
.
Interesting how we learn life lessons from cooking. I didn’t have enough patience to beat the egg whites thoroughly the first time as I just wanted to get it over and done with quickly. As a result, the omelette didn’t turn out fluffy. Because of my experience, I knew today that I needed to be patient in beating the egg whites and I was rewarded with much fluffier omelette than I had the first time. #gratitudediary
.
.
.
